OL,3,CCampaigners warn holiday park could
OL,4,Cdamage 'sensitive habitat' for rare
OL,5,Cwildlife
OL,7,FTim Scott went to Roanhead beach to
OL,8,Ffind out why protesters are opposing
OL,9,Fthe new holiday park.
OL,11,FProtesters are looking to end plans to
OL,12,Fbuild a new holiday park they say
OL,13,Fcould destroy the unique habitat that
OL,14,Fsupports rare plants and wildlife.
OL,16,FThe Save Roanhead campaigners are
OL,17,Fcalling on the to reject the proposed
OL,18,Fplans for the 230-lodge holiday park,
OL,19,Fwhich would be built next to Roanhead
OL,20,Fbeach.
