OL,7,FThe beach is just a few miles north of
OL,8,F, and is the home of a number of rare
OL,9,Fplants and animals, including the
OL,10,Fnatterjack toad.
OL,12,FDarren Mason, a member of the , said:
OL,13,F"We have between 18 and 25% of the
OL,14,Fwhole of the UK population.
OL,16,F"It's designated as an important plant
OL,17,Farea, for its botanical richness and
OL,18,Frare habitats."
