OL,3,CCampaigners warn holiday park could
OL,4,Cdamage 'sensitive habitat' for rare
OL,5,Cwildlife
OL,7,FMore than 8,000 people have signed a
OL,8,Fpetition calling on the Westmorland
OL,9,Fand Furness Council to reject the
OL,10,Fproposal from ILM Group, and a
OL,11,Fdecision is expected in May 2024.
OL,13,FDevelopers originally wanted to build
OL,14,Fup to 450 lodges on the site, but
OL,15,Fafter strong pushback from locals ILM
OL,16,FGroup scaled back their plans.
