OL,7,FIn a statement, the ILM Group said:
OL,8,F"We have been in constructive dialogue
OL,9,Fwith Natural England to ensure that
OL,10,Fthe revised plans are sustainable and
OL,11,Fsensitive to the local environment.
OL,13,F"The resort will be managed under
OL,14,Fspecific environmental standards with
OL,15,Fmeasures in place to ensure that
OL,16,Fstaff, suppliers, and visitors to the
OL,17,Fresort respect their surroundings."
